Can I talk about a Man Crush even if it isn't Monday??? Of course I can. It's my account I can do what I want. So let's talk about @revciancio shall we!!!! He put me on my first podcast and exposed me and @eatfamous to a whole new world of people. He allowed me to help promote New YorkCity Burger week all the way from Toronto. He also made sure that when I was in NY I met just about everyone in the food scene who matter and organized the most epic food crawl I've been on all in honour of my trip. Furthermore he's a great dude with a passion for food and one of my favs on or off the gram. So yeah, here's a shoutout to my buddy @revciancio and check out this pick of these Pig Style Fries from @grinderz that he took!!
